reviewText: Love exploration of Stranger Among US'S Hassidic culture, Clever mystery. Melanie Griffith a bit over the top but Eric Thall was perfect.
Title: One Good Cop & A Stranger Among Us + Veronica Guerin - TF

reviewText: Love all three movies and getting 3 in one is a great value, plus it saves space in the media cabinet. The Veronica Guerin DVD is on its own. The first two movies are on the same DVD. All are great to watch and add to an existing collection.
Title: One Good Cop & A Stranger Among Us + Veronica Guerin - TF

reviewText: These three movies will be among my favorites in my home library....they were in excellent condition and viewed perfectly....my only drawback was the fact that there were NO subtitles involved.....I always appreciate that for any movie I watch as I have to keep my volume low, living in an apartment complex and liking to watch movies late at night when I have time!
summary: Three awesome movies in one case...
Title: One Good Cop & A Stranger Among Us + Veronica Guerin - TF

reviewText: These three movies are really interesting to watch.  Two give you a view into what you are unlikely to know well. The other shows what a good man can be brought to do do for those he loves. Not just any movies.
Title: One Good Cop & A Stranger Among Us + Veronica Guerin - TF

reviewText: Getting these three movies for one price was truly a bargain. My husband wanted One Good Cop, so that is why I ordered it. The other two movies are very good also.
Title: One Good Cop & A Stranger Among Us + Veronica Guerin - TF

reviewText: Interesting plot in these movies, but a bit dated when compared with more recent movies with similar themes.Very reasonable price, if you are a fan of Michael Keaton, Melanie Griffin.
Title: One Good Cop & A Stranger Among Us + Veronica Guerin - TF
